        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>District of Columbia Courts Vacancy Reduction Act</b></p> <p>This bill allows District of Columbia judicial nominees to be appointed after a 30-day congressional review period without the advice and consent of the Senate, unless a joint resolution of disapproval is enacted into law during that period.</p>]]>
        </text>
